name: "sounds-back"
displayName: "Give me the sounds back!"
author: "adam74 (ALLT, adame74)"
subtitle: "Replaces new sounds with old ones"
description: "Starting from version 154, most in-game sounds have been completely replaced. This mod replaces sounds with their old equivalent (if any) or removes them completely. If you're not a fan of the new sounds, this mod is for you."
version: "1.0"
minGameVersion: "154"
hidden: true
